nodes.text: MF-80 was a protocol droid with feminine programming who was in the service of the Grand Hutt Council and owned by Gardulla.

MF-80 was voiced by Angelique Perrin, who also voiced Adi Gallia and Mama the Hutt in Star Wars: The Clone Wars TV series. She replaced TC-70, Jabba's protocol droid, who was originally intended to appear.
